## Common Mistakes

**ŌØī DON'T:**
- Raw `<button>` ŌĆö always use shadcn `<Button>`
- Paste Figma values directly (`#2563EB`, `bg-[#2563EB]`)
- Hardcode colors, spacing, or stroke widths
- Skip `md:` variants ŌĆö every component must scale
- Big breakpoint jumps (`px-4 lg:px-32`)
- Build for desktop first, then try to shrink to mobile
- `style={{ width: X, height: X }}` for dimensions ŌĆö inline styles bypass Tailwind's responsive system entirely. Use `size-*`, `w-*`, `h-*` classes so `md:` variants remain available
- `text-[18px]`, `text-[25px]` without an `md:` pair ŌĆö use the typography table above or approve the exception explicitly (constrained native-style components only)

**Ō£ģ DO:**
